{"tid":2449741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「美國隊長」容偉業刑滿出獄 即致電嫲嫲報平安","createTime":"2021-03-17T02:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T07:47:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":92,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f888b59e6747839b84cc965f4ca06e862a4da5a0","tid":2449741,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet/12559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet%2F12559&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=500e661f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet/12559</a><br />\n<br />\n綽號「美國隊長」的容偉業，在2016年旺角騷亂中被陪審團裁定兩項暴動及一項襲警罪成，被判監禁3年。容今於赤柱監獄服刑完畢，早上有約20名親友及支持者到監獄外「接放學」。深水埗區議會副主席伍月蘭、屯門區議員盧俊宇及東區區議員曾健成亦有到場。<br />\n<br />\n約9時40分，容偉業穿上當年每天上庭穿著的西裝和灰色領呔，捧著沉重的「包頭袋」。由懲教人員帶離監獄閘門外。容見到大家後不斷說：「Hello hello」、「多謝大家關心！」<br />\n<br />\n容向在場傳媒表示：「之後想見多啲屋企人」，亦想重過正常生活，「其他嘢我唔想做太多」。不過轉過頭也說：「希望想做多啲對香港有公益的事。」<br />\n<br />\n容之後立即打電話給嫲嫲及家人報平安，旁人叮囑他與朋友食過早餐後便要回去見嫲嫲，容回應道：「返屋企先搵佢啦！」<br />\n<br />\n他表示自己在獄中有看關於社運的書，此外「《國安法》、初選的事都知道」，「但詳細唔方便講太多。」他又笑言今天「出冊果吓好匆忙」，不時道：「香港人加油！」"},{"pid":"1651acdd30ed42c231780e1321a2170fcd6fbcb1","tid":2449741,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43b722f7ca4e7650a004e7e39f9199c2a1d34cc","tid":2449741,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfd1164df8d12e7dac8193423e81235e784c972","tid":2449741,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59960c03144f406abd9bd5aadb0b323718a5a47e","tid":2449741,"uid":215700,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"天佑義士"},{"pid":"108e4f3d30625ca124cc390a66abd135a4a2728f","tid":2449741,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"身在囹圄手足知道呢一兩年癲過坐過山車，但可以做很少係咩感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e0fdb94b61996ccc28757fef4cd19304dd1d2a","tid":2449741,"uid":129466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b742da5c55fceb25467ab958846f46425344c5","tid":2449741,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"去下旅行啦"},{"pid":"15f8773853e146dd23f83a7b2bdf76564b03a8f9","tid":2449741,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好休息，感謝付出"},{"pid":"5a22a9d1ad256cdaa8381329788472a0d7aeadac","tid":2449741,"uid":240362,"like":11,"di